    <title>Butterfly主题安装笔记</title>
    <link href="https://starkang1.top/archives/19876/"/>
    <id>https://starkang1.top/archives/19876/</id>
    <published>2022-01-19T06:56:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-01-19T08:35:06.546Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Git的安装"><a href="#Git的安装" class="headerlink" title="Git的安装"></a>Git的安装</h1><p>参考<a href="https://www.runoob.com/git/git-tutorial.html">Git教程</a></p><h1 id="Node-js安装"><a href="#Node-js安装" class="headerlink" title="Node.js安装"></a>Node.js安装</h1><p>Hexo是基于nodejs编写的，所以需要安装nodejs和nodejs 自带一个被称为 npm的<strong>命令行工具</strong>。</p><p>安装参照<a href="https://www.runoob.com/nodejs/nodejs-install-setup.html">Node.js教程</a>。</p><p>安装完成后可以按win+R，</p><p>![<a href="https://gitee.com/xu-weijian/pic-go/raw/master/img/KZE$@%7B[PDNPV_227N%7D[2GIS.jpg]()">https://gitee.com/xu-weijian/pic-go/raw/master/img/KZE$@{[PDNPV_227N}[2GIS.jpg]()</a></p><p>在弹出的对话框入CMD后点确定即运行“命令提示符”窗口</p><p><img src="" alt="https://gitee.com/xu-weijian/pic-go/raw/master/img/LD`HRSY_W)F0`S6L7LH3T2O.png"></p><p>在此界面输入</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>出现版本信息即为安装成功</p><p>![<a href="https://gitee.com/xu-weijian/pic-go/raw/master/img/%7B3N%60%7B%7D]VTX%7DOU%7DRG_SKOUK0.png]()">https://gitee.com/xu-weijian/pic-go/raw/master/img/{3N`{}]VTX}OU}RG_SKOUK0.png]()</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
